{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/54039", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/54039/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/54039/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/54039/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/54039", "id": 358178953, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUzNTgxNzg5NTM=", "number": 54039, "title": "Bounds check on const/static arrays are not eliminated", "user": {"login": "kornelski", "id": 72159, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjcyMTU5", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/72159?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski", "html_url": "https://github.com/kornelski", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 108333, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxMDgzMzM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-LLVM", "name": "A-LLVM", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: Code generation parts specific to LLVM. Both correctness bugs and optimization-related issues."}, {"id": 113376, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxMTMzNzY=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/I-slow", "name": "I-slow", "color": "e10c02", "default": false, "description": "Problems and improvements with respect to performance of generated code."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2018-09-07T19:07:38Z", "updated_at": "2018-12-18T22:53:35Z", "closed_at": "2018-12-18T22:53:34Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "The compiler is smart enough to eliminate bounds check on a slice from a function argument, but not on a slice from a global array.\r\n\r\nHere, as expected, `s[index]` bounds check is eliminated after compiler sees `s.get(index+2)` succeed:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\npub fn elide1(s: &[u8], index: u32) -> u8 {\r\n    let index = index as usize;\r\n    if let Some(&len) = s.get(index+2) {\r\n        s[index] \r\n    } else {0}\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever, the same code, but with `const` array instead of a slice, does have a bounds check:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nconst s: [u8; 5] = [1,2,3,4,5];\r\n\r\npub fn elide2(index: u32) -> u8 {\r\n    let index = index as usize;\r\n    if let Some(&len) = s.get(index+2) {\r\n        s[index] \r\n    } else {0}\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nTested on rustc 1.30.0-nightly (6e0f1cc15 2018-09-05) \r\n\r\nThe globals are poisonous for this optimization. `let slice = &global[..];` doesn't help. Even the slice-using function that usually optimizes well, becomes worse if it gets inlined at a call site using a global.\r\n\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "kornelski", "id": 72159, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjcyMTU5", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/72159?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski", "html_url": "https://github.com/kornelski", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kornelski/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/54039/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/54039/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}